.fixed-width
  h2 Welcome

  p. 
    The Addison County Fair & Field Days Board extends a cordial invitation to you, and your friends and family to exhibit at this year’s 
    Addison County Fair & Field Days on August 6, 7, 8, 9, 10, 2024. It is our pleasure to present the opportunity for area citizens to
    showcase the quality products which they have produced. The guidelines and rules are in this booklet for anyone wishing to enter
    something in the competitive exhibit departments.
  p. 
    We extend our sincere appreciation to all who have exhibited in the past, and look forward to working with new, as well as past
    exhibitors, during our 2024 fair.
  p
